# Shared packages (`packages/*`)

- **Purpose:** Types, Zod (or equivalent) schemas, and constants shared by `apps/api` and `apps/web`.
- **Imports:** No Node-only APIs (`fs`, `path`, etc.) in code consumed by the browser unless the package is explicitly server-only and not depended on by `apps/web`.
- **Money/time:** Same rules as global standards—no float money; document serialization expectations for API boundaries.
- **Naming:** Keep package boundaries stable; prefer small, explicit exports over barrel files that hide circular dependencies.
